org.ecoinformatics.seek.querybuilder

Class DBSelectTableModelItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ecoinformatics.seek.querybuilder.DBSelectTableModelItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, DBDisplayItemIFace, DSTableFieldIFace
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DBWhereListCellBase

    public class DBSelectTableModelItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, DBDisplayItemIFace
    This class represents each row in the JTable that enables the user to select a specific field in table and any additional information that can be changed. The mDisplayItem data member will hold a valid pointer to an object in the schema in the Advanced version, but not in the Standard.
